---
title: Venue - PyCon India 2025
description: PyCon India 2025 Venue at Nimhans Convention Center
layout: base.njk
---
{% from "components/button.njk" import button %}
{% from "components/venueCard.njk" import venueCard %}

<header>
    {% set activePage = 'venue' %} 
</header>

<div class="w-full h-auto -mb-20 bg-pycon-blue">
    <div class="pt-[200px] mx-[5%] md:mx-[145px]">
        <div class="black-han-sans-regular font-normal text-3xl md:text-5xl md:text-center text-[#FFFFFF] text-center lg:text-left">
            Nimhans Convention Center
        </div>

        <div class="absolute top-2/5 right-4 md:block">
            <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/star-lime-vector.svg" alt="Groovy star" class="md:w-16 md:h-16 w-10 h-10">
        </div>

        <div class="absolute md:top-3/4 pt-52 md:right-20 right-12 md:block">
            <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/star-pink-vector.svg" alt="Groovy star" class="md:w-16 md:h-16 w-10 h-10">
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:space-x-8 lg:justify-between">
            <div class="space-grotesk-regular font-medium text-xl lg:text-sm xl:text-2xl md:text-2xl pt-8 text-[#FFFFFF] text-center lg:text-left">
                <p>Nimhans Convention Center,</p>
                <p>Hosur Road, Lakkasandra,</p>
                <p>Bengaluru - 560029</p>
                <p>Landmark: Near Dairy Circle</p>
                <div class="pt-8">{{ button(text="Find Direction", url="https://maps.app.goo.gl/jwUM4FYX6G35YkYe7?g_st=com.google.maps.preview.copy", lime_bg=true, env = env) }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-[90%] lg:w-[70%] xl:w-[52%] pt-24 pr-4 mx-auto lg:ml-auto">
                {{ venueCard(bg="lime", venueData=venue.location, env=env) }}
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<div class="w-full bg-lavender">
    <div class="pt-[100px] mx-[5%] md:mx-[145px] md:pt-44">
        <div class="black-han-sans-regular pt-32 lg:pt-20 xl:pt-32 md:pt-56 md:text-center font-normal text-3xl md:text-5xl text-[#000000] text-center lg:text-left">
            <p>Getting to the</p>
            <p>Conference Venue</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-32 relative flex flex-col md:flex-row">
            <div class="flex-grow">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                    <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/train.svg" alt="Train" class="h-10 ml-0 md:h-16 lg:h-28 mx-auto md:mx-0">
                </div>
                <div class="w-[80%] lg:w-[60%] xl:w-[50%] ml-auto xl:mr-[12%] -mt-20 lg:-mt-40">
                    {{ venueCard(bg="lime", venueData=venue.metro, env=env) }}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-24 relative flex flex-col md:flex-row">
            <div class="flex-grow">
                <div class="w-[80%] lg:w-[60%] xl:w-[60%] flex-shrink-0">
                    {{ venueCard(bg="purple", venueData=venue.bus, env=env) }}
                </div>
                <div class="mx-auto pl-40 flex items-center justify-center -mt-20 lg:-mt-40 z-10 relative" style="pointer-events: none;">
                    <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/bus.svg" alt="Bus" class="h-40 lg:h-56">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="pt-32 w-full lg:w-2/3 xl:w-1/2 text-justify pb-40">
            <p class="p-4 font-normal text-lg md:text-xl space-grotesk-regular leading-8">
                Located centrally in Bengaluru, the venue has 2 floors. The ground floor, has all the main tracks happening in 3 halls as per schedule. There is a booth area, community space and beverage stalls. The first floor has open spaces, poster sessions, Birds of a Feather, and more happening.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="hidden md:block pt-40 xl:pt-32 w-full justify-center pl-12 md:pl-4 xl:pl-36">
            <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/auto.svg" alt="Auto" class="h-24 md:h-44">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
